{"tid":2184598,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［一國一制］強國猿 林公公 馬道立 你割撚曾表明香港存在三權分立","createTime":"2020-09-01T15:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T16:13:10.000Z","uid":189564,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e502d2923f035546ca9d58b113ec9fada891ca","tid":2184598,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nTn3vE6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnTn3vE6.png&h=fa4d40ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xqD30e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xqD30e.png&h=f3e38280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前d官都仲有人性 未狗官得哂<br />\n林鄭幾時宣佈香港正名香港市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faeacaf34b52a720bbe88b5d8d31d7fe6897db3a","tid":2184598,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50942e368945e2f7e2ed4885922ae79b18daedcf","tid":2184598,"uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"本土研究社今日（9月1日）「正本清源」指，在本港立法機關中首次有人提出「三權分立」，是出自1984年，由時任親英派立法局議員、現任基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠所提出。她指，要維持未來香港安定與繁榮，有賴「立法、司法、行政三權分立的政治架構」。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QcV6gi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QcV6gi.jpg&h=8f3a5933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource hk01"},{"pid":"2693820409609f70dca62c5ea499dd8e6bc9a674","tid":2184598,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"記得backup新聞呀！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2292a46c978325442d1ffd54f84f05412c3504ff","tid":2184598,"uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"《立場新聞》翻查司法機構網站，「三權分立」、「separation of powers」分別在判詞等文件出現逾百次。明年即將接任終審法院首席法官的張舉能，亦曾在 2008 年的判詞中表明《基本法》確立三權分立原則。<br />\n<br />\n張舉能判詞提「separation of powers」<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》記者在司法機構網站搜尋關鍵字「三權分立」，發現此四字在判詞等文件出現了 129 次；「separation of powers」出現 145 次；而「separation of power」則出現 13 次。<br />\n其中一宗案件，一名前基金經理陸家祥需於市場失當行為審裁處接受內幕交易研訊，他申請司法覆核挑戰審裁處的司法管轄權。在 2008 年 11 月 18 日，高等法院決定駁回其司法覆核申請。<br />\n<br />\n時任高等法院原訟法庭法官張舉能在判詞中，曾經多次提及「separation of powers」。在判詞第 29 段，張舉能清楚表明「separation of powers」原則是受《基本法》保障，特區的司法權完全屬於司法機構：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>翻案喇翻案喇</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"8712b995a221ddc0f34f33e213e31bcce83cd859","tid":2184598,"uid":94591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"強国猿同林公公都上神檯<br />\n<br />\n如果十年前高登巴絲坐時光機黎到2020一定會痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff10a4ba84c32f8dbd330b0c199f8b0eaf5cd36d","tid":2184598,"uid":341817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"嗰啲都係歷史文件 不再具有任何現實意義架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>今天的我打倒昨天的我</del>"},{"pid":"85de2458120952e9daa29d1b2a3cc0bb7923c733","tid":2184598,"uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8712b995a221ddc0f34f33e213e31bcce83cd859","tid":2184598,"uid":94591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"強国猿同林公公都上神檯<br />\n<br />\n如果十年前高登巴絲坐時光機黎到2020一定會痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"錯錯錯 依加係坐時光機番左清朝<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">愛新覺羅 維尼</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LuUCr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LuUCr6.jpg&h=2a73adf4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}